                  handling for education programs was investigated in an ABA
                  study design using the same measures of welfare in armadillos
                  (N = 10), hedgehogs (N = 12), and red-tailed hawks (N = 6) at
                  11 AZA institutions. Mixed model analysis revealed FGM and
                  undesirable behaviors did not differ between groups in
                  Experiment One (FGM [μg/g feces]: Median[Interquartile Range]
                  education: 28.49[21.05-42.29], exhibit: 30.38[26.33–42.56],
